<pc>，</pc>乃弘治<num value="0">甲子</num>邑人袁銛所撰<pc>。</pc>名繼前志<pc>，</pc>實則體例各殊<pc>。</pc>△<pc>《</pc>
<title>毗陵志</title>
<pc>》</pc>
<measure quantity="40" unit="chapters">
<num value="40">四十</num>卷</measure>
